{"tid":605831,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實從你一出世開始，就已經係名賭徒","createTime":"2018-03-26T04:17:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-27T01:18:21.000Z","uid":74202,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"feb90631515cd88100ad175d4369a4e11fe38822","tid":605831,"uid":74202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T04:17:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">人生嘅本質根本就係場賭博</span></span><br />\n從你自出娘胎戈刻起<br />\n遊戲亦都正式開始<br />\n<br />\n你出世賭有冇遺傳病<br />\n係咪含住金鎖匙出事<br />\n賭贏左就呢世油鹽柴米唔駛憂，贏在起跑線上<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">正</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n去到讀書，押上18年的努力去考個乜春dse<br />\n贏左就入大學就威啦，簡直人生贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又hea又fing到僅僅夠分畢業都有人請你<br />\n大學生喎，社會棟樑阿嘛～<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">爽</span></span><br />\n<br />\n愛情同婚姻亦係一場賭局<br />\n挖左自己個心出黎<br />\n押上你對佢嘅愛<br />\n期望得到佢嘅感動同回應<br />\n一係有，一係乜都冇，甚至可能連本都輸埋<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">慘</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">慢慢你變成左一個變態賭徒<br />\n每日都不停咁係到落注碼</span></span><br />\n<br />\n有d人天生就是贏家<br />\n一生風調雨順<br />\n好似陳刀仔咁想要Q就變隻Q出黎，想要女就有女<br />\n係我地眼中都係不費吹灰之力咁就得到<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係，這場人生嘅遊戲就係咁唔公平，亦係佢好玩嘅地方（對係食物鏈頂層嘅人而言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>）</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">吹啊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n亦有d人注定就係潦倒<br />\n係這賭場入面輸到渣都冇得淨<br />\n輸數一兩次都可以賴唔好手風<br />\n一世都輸就只可以認名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你嘅一生就只係住到公屋食m記過世<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">命運</span></span><br />\n<br />\n有人可能會話我太現實主義<br />\n話咩「做野不只係睇成敗，過程先係最重要」<br />\n但我想講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">若果冇成敗，咁過程仲有咩意義可言？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n問心<br />\n你生活嘅每個興奮和沮喪<br />\n都係建構在一個個開大開小的「賭局」<br />\n考試合唔合格，佢接唔接受你嘅求婚... ...<br />\n<br />\n係人生呢個永無休止嘅賭博中<br />\n當我意識到呢個無限loop想抽身嘅時候<br />\n先發覺<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">一切已經太遲</span></span>"},{"pid":"078008202543969b1779d280c3dadb3527247072","tid":605831,"uid":136835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T04:19:04.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"0a3a01fb6a4ce78c1898854a0af37c5ca0026821","tid":605831,"uid":38358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T04:26:40.000Z","msg":"咁你戒賭未？"},{"pid":"6dd75c14891754ca78cbf75381a5790b07cbe082","tid":605831,"uid":132524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T04:29:53.000Z","msg":"應該點先可以唔賭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b68f3bb4f363d385d7f2f6b9d0575f3a41c3897","tid":605831,"uid":147739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T04:33:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該點先可以唔賭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有得唔賭咩? <br />\n根本做任何一個決定都要衡量唔同後果<br />\n衡量完先再決定<br />\n就當你得一個後果 其實只不過係all-in <br />\nso what's the difference? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"776f9055fe42650b56f7eb9ed52612039e3fb2de","tid":605831,"uid":74202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b68f3bb4f363d385d7f2f6b9d0575f3a41c3897","tid":605831,"uid":147739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T04:33:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該點先可以唔賭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有得唔賭咩? <br />\n根本做任何一個決定都要衡量唔同後果<br />\n衡量完先再決定<br />\n就當你得一個後果 其實只不過係all-in <br />\nso what's the difference? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T01:14:48.000Z","msg":"啱，其實你已經返唔到轉頭。年紀越大，賭注亦會越來越大。"},{"pid":"df182eb504ce6d124d601530872842cfa706ef64","tid":605831,"uid":74202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a3a01fb6a4ce78c1898854a0af37c5ca0026821","tid":605831,"uid":38358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T04:26:40.000Z","msg":"咁你戒賭未？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T01:18:21.000Z","msg":"唔會戒到架，你嘅人生係充斥住無數賭博<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}